headline: Kroger expands DoorDash partnership to offer full grocery selection nationwide
summary: The expanded offering comes as Kroger looks to keep growing its digital business, which accounts for nearly 9% of the company’s total sales revenue.

headline: DoorDash (DASH): A Fresh Look at Valuation After Recent Tech Sector Pullback
summary: DoorDash (DASH) shares have moved lower following a recent pullback in the broader tech sector. With the stock still up more than 60% year to date, many are watching to see if momentum resumes. See our latest analysis for DoorDash. DoorDash's share price has come off its highs this week after a stellar run, but the 12% gain over the past month signals that momentum could still be in play. With a 62% year-to-date share price return and a huge 93% total shareholder return over the past year,...
